  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d918767056243b606f992\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64011f301e9e2e54bfd9d640\" /> <a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/autopickup.58007/updates\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d919167056243b606f998\" />  </a> <a href=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/AutoPickup+\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d919167056243b606f996\" />  </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/640d919167056243b606f994\" />  </a>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/64a421d04776b941b5a1f5ff\" />\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/638a91e9aa2989386ab8ef79\" />  </a>\n\n</center>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Full Transcript</summary>\n\nAutopickup+\nA minimalist east to setup pickup plugin!\n\nSNAPPY AND MINDLESS\nThe plugin comes with a fully functional out of the box experience!\n\nSetup is snappy, getting the plugin in a functional state with just 4 lines of config!\n\nCUSTOMIZABLE\nEvery aspect is configurable, without being overloaded!\n\nThis plugin integrates the fully customizable messages protocol. Send clickable components, make chat menus, send URL's and more!\n</details>\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/EgUdCD8dKhg2H0QQLwwkCAsGIB03B08oNgAFCBYZLB03\" />",
